name: Fast delivery (kileurixix)
description:
Deliver some food, fast !

Roam the neighborhood to find an order, go to the appropriate store, then deliver it !

Warning, there is policemen around the red lights!

[Arrows] to move

[space] to order a command

[space] to deliver

[enter] to begin

[enter] to retry

tips : hotdog shop on the left, burger in middle, chicken on the right
